reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 338/02: NON-APPLICATION OF PART III OF THE MUNICIPAL AFFAIRS ACT
reg_info.reg_name_text: NON-APPLICATION OF PART III OF THE MUNICIPAL AFFAIRS ACT
reg_info.act_under: Town of Moosonee Act, 2000   Loi de 2000 sur la ville de Moosonee

content.content: 1. For the purposes of section 5 of the Act, Part III of the Municipal Affairs Act ceases to apply to the Town of Moosonee. O. Reg. 338/02, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. For the purposes of section 5 of the Act, Part III of the Municipal Affairs Act ceases to apply to the Town of Moosonee. O. Reg. 338/02, s. 1.

content.content: 2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Regulation). O. Reg. 338/02, s. 2.
